      <title>美国威胁实施战争制裁，中国对俄罗斯出口大幅下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/china-s-exports-to-russia-slump-amid-us-threat-of-war-sanctions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[3月份，中国对俄罗斯的出口大幅下滑，这是自2022年中期以来的首次同比下降，原因是美国越来越多地威胁称，如果中国的商品帮助莫斯科入侵乌克兰，就会对北京进行报复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/china-s-exports-to-russia-slump-amid-us-threat-of-war-sanctions</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
